195
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:16,360
and void.

196
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:18,840
When you do,

197
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:22,120
love yourself

198
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,000
and the world

199
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,480
